name: Sherrie Davis
description:
Hello my name is Sherrie Davis, am 30 years old single with no kid, am from Dallas Texas USA.
I’m looking for a man that is honest, trusting, loving, kind, caring and faithfulness, because that’s the best qualities in a relationship. Its have being a little over seven years since I have dated anyone. With all honesty, I am looking for a very serious long term relationship without any head games.
